Package: pyCOMPASSR
Title: API to 'Python' Library 'pyCOMPASS'
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Marco Moretto <marco.moretto@fmach.it> [aut]", 
    "Paolo Sonego <paolo.sonego@fmach.it> [aut, cre]"
  ))
URL: https://github.com/onertipaday/pyCOMPASSR
Maintainer: Paolo Sonego <paolo.sonego@gmail.com>
Description: Using the R package 'reticulate', this package creates an interface to the 'pyCOMPASS' python library.
  pyCOMPASS is a Python interface to COMPASS, the gene expression compendia GraphQL endpoint.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: reticulate,
  xml2
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
SystemRequirements: 'python3' needs to built for the same architecture R is built for (32 or 64 bit).
